17
00:03:14,690 --> 00:03:15,120
Lu Zheng.

18
00:03:16,110 --> 00:03:17,240
We're colleagues after all.

19
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,880
We don't want to beat you.

20
00:03:20,060 --> 00:03:20,870
Just admit it.

21
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,510
Then we can save the time

22
00:03:22,829 --> 00:03:24,460
and arrange Xie Kengran’s funeral.

23
00:03:24,740 --> 00:03:25,310
Wang,

24
00:03:25,620 --> 00:03:28,250
a rebel like this has appeared in the Investigation Bureau.

25
00:03:28,490 --> 00:03:30,550
How can we keep our heads up outside?

26
00:03:35,100 --> 00:03:35,530
My Lord.

27
00:03:36,670 --> 00:03:37,680
Flog him 50 times. Beat him hard.

28
00:03:37,970 --> 00:03:38,400
My Lord.

29
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,070
If a noble young man makes a mistake,

30
00:03:44,110 --> 00:03:45,390
he should be punished in the the same way as a commoner.

31
00:03:45,530 --> 00:03:47,890
I'm just afraid that someone will gossip behind us,

32
00:03:49,140 --> 00:03:49,760
and say that

33
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:50,829
with abuse of illegal punishment,

34
